data.description: Property has been leased for a year, rent is $2,300 a month with $2,500 security deposit /utilities not included in rent.  Only investors at this time.  Lakefront with a dock! so bring your water toys.  This 3 bedroom/2bath/2car garage open floor plan home is what you are looking for.  Concrete Block construction, built in 2002 this home features a newer roof (5 years new), solar panels, split floor plan, and easy access to 417 and 528.  This property is located near shopping, dining, great schools and universities. Only a short drive to Disney World and Orlando International Airport. Buyer must assume solar panels loan with purchase (monthly rate $147.00 and balance is +-$19,000).  Savings galore with an entire house solar system.  Be green! Conserve energy.  24 hr. notice is required to show please. Agents please see Realtor Only remarks for showing instructions (must contact agent).
